                    <div class="mt-3 p-2 bg-white rounded-md border border-indigo-200">
                        <span class="font-bold text-indigo-700">ğŸ¥— ìƒì„¸ ê±´ê°• ì •ë³´:</span>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-1 text-sm">
                            <span class="text-gray-700">ğŸ”¥ ì¹¼ë¡œë¦¬: ${health.calories || 'N/A'}</span>
                            <span class="text-gray-700">ğŸ’ª ë‹¨ë°±ì§ˆ: ${health.protein || 'N/A'}</span>
